Class AbstractMessageSender

java.lang.Object
  com.sun.enterprise.mgmt.transport.AbstractMessageSender
All Implemented Interfaces:
MessageSender, ShoalMessageSender
Direct Known Subclasses:
GrizzlyTCPConnectorWrapper
public abstract class AbstractMessageSender
extends java.lang.Object
implements MessageSender

This class implements a common MessageSender logic simply in order to help the specific transport layer to be implemented easily Mainly, this stores both source's PeerID and target's PeerID before sending the message to the peer

Author:
Bongjae Chang
